results.deck: Nihon Bussan Co., Ltd. more commonly known as Nichibutsu is a Japanese publisher and developer.
results.description:
Nichibutsu was founded in 1970 and started developing video games in 1978.

They are best know in Japan for various adult Mahjong games and the F1 Circus racing series. Their biggest US succcess came in 1990 with the release of WCW World Championship Wrestling on the NES a WCW reskin of their 1989 release Super Star Pro Wrestling.
